text: Vikash Ranjan (born 15 February 1993) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Bihar in the 2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. He made his first-class debut for Bihar in the 2018–19 Ranji Trophy on 1 November 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Bihar cricketers Category:People from Muzaffarpur
